<apex:page renderAs="pdf" contentType="application/pdf" applyBodyTag="false" standardController="Additional_Charges__c" >
    <html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
        <head>
            <style>
                body {
                    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
                    font-size: 12pt;
                    line-height: 1.5;
                }
                .section {
                    margin-bottom: 20px;
                }
                .signature {
                    margin-top: 50px;
                }
                .note {
                    margin-top: 30px;
                    font-size: 10pt;
                    font-style: italic;
                }
            </style>
        </head>
        <body>
            <div class="section">
                <p>Date: <apex:outputText value="{0,date,dd/MM/yyyy}"> <apex:param value="{!TODAY()}" /> </apex:outputText></p>
                <p>To<br/>
                {!Additional_Charges__c.Booking__r.salutation_Applicant1__c} {!Additional_Charges__c.Booking__r.First_Applicant_Name__c}<br/>
                  {!Additional_Charges__c.Booking__r.Communication_address__c}<br/>
                  Mobile No.: {!Additional_Charges__c.Booking__r.Mobile_Primary1__c}<br/>
                  EMail ID: {!Additional_Charges__c.Booking__r.Email1__c}</p>
            </div>

            <div class="section">
                <p><strong>Subject:</strong> Stage Intimation/Payment demand - Flat No. {!Additional_Charges__c.Booking__r.Plot__r.Name} on the {!Additional_Charges__c.Booking__r.Plot__r.Floor__c} floor  at {!Additional_Charges__c.Booking__r.Plot__r.Project__r.Name}, {!Additional_Charges__c.Booking__r.Plot__r.Project__r.Project_Address__c}</p>
            </div>

            <div class="section">
                <p>Dear Sir/Madam,</p>
                <p>We would like to bring to your kind attention that an amount of <strong>Rs. <apex:outputText value="{0, number, ###,###,###}"><apex:param value="{!Additional_Charges__c.Amount__c}" /> </apex:outputText>/-</strong> <!--(<strong>Rupees )</strong>-->
                    is due towards the “<strong>Additional Charges</strong>”, as per the agreed payment schedule for Flat No.  {!Additional_Charges__c.Booking__r.Plot__r.Name} located on the{!Additional_Charges__c.Booking__r.Plot__r.Floor__c} Floor at <strong>{!Additional_Charges__c.Booking__r.Plot__r.Project__r.Name}</strong>,{!Additional_Charges__c.Booking__r.Plot__r.Project__r.Project_Address__c}.</p>

                <p>Kindly arrange to make the payment in favour of:</p>

                <p>
                    {payeeName}<br/>
                    {bankDetails}
                </p>

                <p>As per the terms &amp; conditions agreed between us, this payment has to be made within 15 days of this intimation. Should you require any clarification, please feel free to contact the undersigned between 2:30 PM – 5:30 PM on all working days.</p>

                <p>We thank you for your continued cooperation and assure you of our best services at all times.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="signature">
                <p>Yours faithfully,<br/>
                For Jain House,</p>

                <br/><br/>
                <p>CRM</p>
            </div>

            <div class="note">
                Note: Delayed payments will attract an interest of 18% per annum, applicable at the time of handover.
            </div>
        </body>
    </html>
</apex:page>